super_trans is an offline translation program

It uses "Apertium", which can do offline translation.

You can do translation anywhere with it.


It generates a webpage from the input text that not only has all language translations embedded in it, it dynamically adjusts the website page content to the web browser's "current language".











You need to have a folder called "translation_folder" in your home folder for it to work.


You can use the resultant HTML on your website, and if the user is Spanish, French, German, etc., then that HTML element would automatically be different.

This is really powerful.

